Add bonsai check-queries --lang <name> [sample_file] subcommand. Validates query files (locals.scm, tags.scm, inlines.scm) for a language. Reports capture presence/absence, capability enablement/disablement. If sample file provided, runs queries and shows match counts per capture. Useful feedback loop for writing inlines.scm. See call-inlining spec "CLI" section.
